name: Attack of the Mutant Cabbages
overview: In this game, with some similarities to games like Dig Dug, you play a farmer that must protect his farm from evil mutated cabbages. Spray your water hose at the cabbages to take them out. The game was programed by Anthony Stiller, while Vanja J. Utne did the music and SFX. The game was released into the public domain in 2016.
